          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "\"Porsche owners are passionate about their cars. This partnership will allow them to share their vehicles with others who share that same level of appreciation. It also gives future Porsche owners who are PCA Test Drive members an opportunity to drive a car they dream of buying,\" Steve Haas, senior manager of DriveShare operations.",
