          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "This partnership is sure to work in favor of both DriveShare and the Porsche Club of America. According to Hargery, PCA currently has more than 135,000 members making it the largest single-marque car club of all time, while Hagerty's DriveShare currently offers users access to more than 4,400 vehicles. To ensure against vehicle damage or injuries, every DriveShare rental comes with $1 million in insurance as well as access to a roadside assistance program tailored toward classic cars.",
